allData.bio: Nandan Srikrishna is a University of Michigan Class of 2025 student who serves as Advocacy Coordinator for Helping Hands: A Students for Students Movement Inc. He has a passion for sciences, music, and volunteering, playing alto saxophone and dedicating over 100 hours at Beaumont Hospital.

Nandan Srikrishna is a member of the University of Michigan Class of 2025 who serves as Advocacy Coordinator for Helping Hands. He has a passion for sciences, music, and volunteering, having dedicated over 100 hours at Beaumont Hospital and being part of the International Academy Varsity Science Olympiad team.
